<title>USA: WestPoint Stevens to repurchase 1 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>WestPoint Stevens to repurchase 1 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>WEST POINT, Ga 1996-08-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>WestPoint Stevens Inc said Monday its board of directors has approved the repurchase of up to one million additional shares of the company's common stock.</p>
<p>The repurchased shares will be used for general corporate purposes, including possible awards under the company's stock-based incentive compensation plans and the company's stock matching under its employee 401(k) plan.</p>
<p>The authorization includes both open market purchases as well as private transactions from time to time, the company said.</p>
